OL,3,CLord Mandelson released on bail
OL,4,Cfollowing arrest
OL,6,FIn a statement issued just after 2am
OL,7,Fon Tuesday, a Metropolitan Police
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "A 72-year-old man
OL,9,Farrested on suspicion of misconduct in
OL,10,Fpublic office has been released on
OL,11,Fbail pending further investigation.
OL,13,F"He was arrested at an address in
OL,14,FCamden on Monday, 23 February and was
OL,15,Ftaken to a London police station for
OL,16,Finterview.
OL,18,F"This follows search warrants at two
OL,19,Faddresses in the Wiltshire and Camden
OL,20,Fareas.
OL,26,@pD@TOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
