OL,3,CLord Mandelson released on bail
OL,4,Cfollowing arrest
OL,6,F"We are not able to provide further
OL,7,Finformation at this stage to prevent
OL,8,Fprejudicing the integrity of the
OL,9,Finvestigation."
OL,11,FFootage on Monday showed Lord
OL,12,FMandelson being escorted out of his
OL,13,Fhouse in Camden by a plain clothes
OL,14,Fpolice officer. The Metropolitan
OL,15,FPolice later confirmed the 72-year-old
OL,16,Fwas interviewed at a London police
OL,17,Fstation.
