OL,3,CLord Mandelson released on bail
OL,4,Cfollowing arrest
OL,6,FLord Mandelson was sacked as US
OL,7,Fambassador in September after Downing
OL,8,FStreet said fresh revelations about
OL,9,Fhis relationship with Epstein had
OL,10,Femerged.
OL,12,FHe resigned from the House of Lords
OL,13,Fearlier this month, following the
OL,14,Frelease of the so-called Epstein
OL,15,Ffiles; however, due to parliamentary
OL,16,Fprocedure, he retains his title.
OL,18,FThe government said on Monday it was
OL,19,Fworking on legislation to remove his
OL,20,Ftitle.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
