OL,3,CLord Mandelson released on bail
OL,4,Cfollowing arrest
OL,6,FLord Mandelson's arrest came shortly
OL,7,Fafter MPs were told the first batch of
OL,8,Fdocuments related to the 72-year-old's
OL,9,Fappointment as US ambassador would be
OL,10,Freleased in early March.
OL,12,FTwo of his properties were previously
OL,13,Fsearched by police in connection with
OL,14,Fthe allegations, which surfaced
OL,15,Ffollowing the US Department of
OL,16,FJustice's document dump related to
OL,17,FEpstein last month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
